{"tid":552324,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"搵巴絲3月一齊去西藏包車！！","createTime":"2018-02-06T11:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T01:28:25.000Z","uid":125546,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2aec8dcd9115b5868096a338ba437be5143e0ae","tid":552324,"uid":125546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"依家我地有三人想包車由西寧玩到拉薩阿里（共20日）有冇巴絲想一齊拼車！架車坐到5個人！而5個人的話就會7000蚊人仔一個人。預計係3月頭出發！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行程會cover到以下既地方：西寧曹家堡接機，西寧休息，1西寧日月山，倒淌河，青海湖，黑馬河，茶卡鹽湖，2.戈壁灘住格尔木，3昆侖山，可可西里，唐古拉山，4住納木措，5住拉薩，6，拉薩，巴松措，住藏族家里，7色季拉山住林芝，8住加查，9雍布拉康，住澤當，10羊卓雍措，卡若拉冰川，日喀則，11珠峰大本营，12住日喀則，13拉薩，仲會去埋阿里（詳情仲同司機傾緊！）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外有冇巴絲可以比下意見個行程有冇得更好或更平既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33af95b2e3919b1a96992504c652270cb65fe114","tid":552324,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb4119f369d588d523e8381e46d2e19c42861a3b","tid":552324,"uid":12104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:34:48.000Z","msg":"預計3月14至3月25到，有無得join 一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0ac6c8b328bee282b4c5976f14708d084034f0","tid":552324,"uid":125546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb4119f369d588d523e8381e46d2e19c42861a3b","tid":552324,"uid":12104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:34:48.000Z","msg":"預計3月14至3月25到，有無得join 一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy